{"id": "chg-001", "source_type": "changelog_row", "upstream_version": "v5.5", "hypothesis": "如果当前仓库使用 HttpClient Digest 认证，并且对接端未完整支持 RFC 7616，或本地代码未处理 nextnonce / rspauth，则升级后可能出现 401 或 nonce 相关认证失败。", "sample_failure_signatures": ["401 Unauthorized", "Invalid nonce", "DigestScheme", "NextNonceInterceptor"], "suspect_apis": ["DigestSchemeFactory", "DigestScheme", "UsernamePasswordCredentials", "HttpClientBuilder.setAuthSchemeRegistry", "NextNonceInterceptor"], "likely_impact_surfaces": ["SAP Gateway 集成", "OData V4 服务接入", "ROMA Connect 调用", "政务外网 REST API 调用"], "before_after_hint": {"before": "new DigestSchemeFactory()", "after": "new DigestSchemeFactory().setAlgorithm(\"SHA-256\") + addInterceptorFirst(new NextNonceInterceptor())"}}
{"id": "chg-002", "source_type": "changelog_row", "upstream_version": "v5.5", "hypothesis": "如果当前仓库启用了 httpclient5-cache 且使用共享缓存，带 Authorization 的响应在包含 public / must-revalidate / s-maxage 时可能被错误共享，导致跨租户缓存污染。", "sample_failure_signatures": ["跨租户返回相同 profile 数据", "缓存命中异常", "共享缓存误用"], "suspect_apis": ["CacheConfig.custom().setSharedCache(true)", "CachingExec", "AsyncCachingExec", "ResponseCachingPolicy"], "likely_impact_surfaces": ["多租户 REST Invoke 节点", "用户资料查询接口", "共享 Redis 缓存"], "before_after_hint": {"before": "CacheConfig.custom().setMaxCacheEntries(1000).build()", "after": "CacheConfig.custom().setMaxCacheEntries(1000).setSharedCache(false).build()"}}
{"id": "chg-003", "source_type": "changelog_row", "upstream_version": "v5.5", "hypothesis": "如果当前仓库使用 Apache HttpClient 自动重定向，并且在请求中手工设置 Authorization 或 Cookie 等敏感头，则升级到 5.5 后遇到 302/3xx 可能不再自动跳转，而是直接失败。", "sample_failure_signatures": ["ClientProtocolException", "Redirect rejected", "Cannot retry request with a non-repeatable request entity"], "suspect_apis": ["HttpClients.createDefault", "HttpClients.custom", "setRedirectStrategy", "disableRedirectHandling", "setHeader(\"Authorization\", ...)", "setHeader(\"Cookie\", ...)"], "likely_impact_surfaces": ["OAuth 2.0 授权码流程", "SSO 单点登录跳转", "API 网关重定向场景"], "before_after_hint": {"before": "HttpClients.createDefault().execute(new HttpGet(url))", "after": "HttpClients.custom().disableRedirectHandling().build() 并手动处理 3xx 响应"}}
